metadata.name: ISOMETRIC
metadata.description:
Relationship between dystopia distric (Red human) cyberpunk city and prosper utopia city (Yellow human) linked with a bridge. 

In 2200 we live in highrise building which full of technology and cybernetic facilities. Many people choose to change their body into data for eternity life while many poor people have to suffer from inequality and live in slum with high polution and poor quality of life.

According to rising of population number. The goverment have to eradicate them by killing baby and disabled population in dystopia slum distric and transfer their body into electric energy for utopia city. This method was applyed for the city to save essential resource for the capitalist.

many innocent have to die because of poor and unfortunately.
